{"PARFAY":[{"def":"By my faith; verily.","pos":""}],"PARFLECHE":[{"def":"A kind of rawhide consisting of hide, esp.","pos":""}],"PARFOCAL":[{"def":"With the lower focal points all in the same plane; -- said of sets of eyepieces so mounted that they may be interchanged without varying the focus of the instrument (as a microscope or telescope) with which they are used.","pos":""}]}